## Verification Plan

### Network Test
1. Confirm each lab switch/router has a unique gateway IP

### Backend API Tests (Postman)
1. Create a gateway mapping: `POST /api/lab-gateways` `{ gateway_ip: "192.168.2.1", laboratory_room: "Laboratory 2" }`
2. `POST /api/browser-activity/heartbeat` with `{ computer_name: "PC1", gateway_ip: "192.168.2.1" }` → expect session to show `laboratory_room: "Laboratory 2"`
3. Repeat from a "Lab 1" gateway — verify `PC1 + 192.168.1.1 → Laboratory 1`
4. `GET /api/browser-activity/online-students` → verify both students show correct lab

### Frontend Test
1. Admin logs in → Lab Management → adds two labs with different gateway IPs
2. Two students log in from different labs on `PC1` → both show `PC1` but different lab rooms
3. Dashboard shows `PC1 — Laboratory 1` and `PC1 — Laboratory 2` simultaneously ✅
